-- Cucumber encourages code re-usability concept --

main area is used by Developers, so we don't want to make any changes
in there, so its fine to delete this area as Testers

test - this is where we should set up our POM (Page Object Model)

There's 2 things we have in every project

- code - java
- non-Java (adding excel/properties file)

coding will be at one place
non java will be at another place

POM (Page Object Model) -
Page object model is a design pattern in which we create object repository






